      <title>新民主党撤回支持 特鲁多政府面临垮台风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/ex-trudeau-ally-jagmeet-singh-says-he-ll-vote-to-bring-government-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贾斯汀·特鲁多的一位前重要盟友表示，他将投票推翻政府，此举可能会导致加拿大在明年初陷入选举，除非总理寻求暂时中止议会。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/ex-trudeau-ally-jagmeet-singh-says-he-ll-vote-to-bring-government-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 16:40:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多与弗里兰的惊人通话引发加拿大政治危机</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/the-call-with-chrystia-freeland-that-threw-justin-trudeau-government-into-crisis</link>
      <description><![CDATA[贾斯汀·特鲁多的政治前途几个月来一直不稳定。但威胁到他加拿大总理职位的事件在几天之内就演变成一场危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/the-call-with-chrystia-freeland-that-threw-justin-trudeau-government-into-crisis</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 15:39:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>约翰逊称美国众议院将于周五就避免政府关门的计划进行投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/house-may-vote-on-temporary-fix-to-stop-shutdown-networks-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[众议院共和党人表示，他们将于周五就资金问题进行投票，以确保政府运转至 3 月 14 日，并提供救灾资金并向农民提供数十亿美元的经济援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-20/house-may-vote-on-temporary-fix-to-stop-shutdown-networks-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 20 Dec 2024 13:37:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>当政府停止支出时，实际上哪些设施会被关闭</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/what-actually-happens-when-the-us-government-shuts-down</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联邦政府停摆可能会造成混乱，数千名工作人员被迫休假，其中大多数人无法按时领到工资。纳税人将得不到回电，在一年中最繁忙的旅行周之一，机场排队的人可能会更多，许多国家公园也将关闭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-19/what-actually-happens-when-the-us-government-shuts-down</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Dec 2024 21:32:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
